Robotti & Company, founded by Bob Robotti, has been in the securities business since 1983.  We specialize in applying our research methodology in identifying undervalued securities. We pride ourselves on our disciplined bottom-up research orientation and offer personalized investment management targeted to our clients’ long-term equity investment needs.  
 
Robotti & Company offers a disciplined investment philosophy derived from over thirty years of experience.  We want clients to have the peace of mind that comes from knowing that their money is intelligently invested.



