          Sep 19, 2016                         - Business Wire                

          Board and Executive Moves      




Robotti & Company Advisors (Robotti Advisors) is pleased to announce that Curtis Jensen has joined the Company as a portfolio manager. Mr. Jensen is the former Chief Investment Officer of Third Avenue Management, where he spent 19 years. Mr. Jensen was an early member of the Third Avenue team,eventually managing the firm's small-cap strategy and becoming co-CIO with the firm's founder,legendary value investor Marty Whitman, before being appointed sole Chief Investment Officer.This Smart N 




